@node register "Registration"

@{b}7 - Registration@{ub}

   Since @{b}g2h@{ub} is mailware, the only thing to do to register yourself
   is simply send me an @{"email" link auteur} or a postcard.

   You should use the g2h web site to do that: 

   http://dept-info.labri.u-bordeaux.fr/~darnis/english/amiga

   then, choose 'my softwares', and 'g2h', you will then see an on-line registration
   text-link in the text.

@endnode

