@node version "Programm history"

@{b}9 - Programm history@{ub}

N.B.:   * means bug fixed
        - means minor update
        + means major update

@{b}* Version 1.32 @{i}(24.06.1998)@{ui} :@{ub}

   - Added BGCOLOR option.
     (Suggested by Peter Hutchison <pjhutch@blizzard.u-net.com>).

   - Improved Workbench support.

   * Removed bugs in Workbench interface.

@{b}* Version 1.31b @{i}(22.06.1998)@{ui} :@{ub}

   - It's exactly the same version as the previous one, except I removed some debug messages
     I forgotten to remove ;-)

   * In the previous version, it was impossible to invoke g2h's options with 'g2h -?'.

@{b}* Version 1.31 @{i}(19.06.1998)@{ui} :@{ub}

   * A lot of bugs removed.

   + Improved support for multiple guide files.

   - The option -i and -f have been renamed respectively as -p and -i.

   - All guide files to convert induce the creation of a new directory named exactly as
     the name of the input guide files. It's better for supporting multiples guide files.
     In each directory created, the main node is converted in a file named 'main.html'.

@{b}* Version 1.3 @{i}(02.12.1997)@{ui} :@{ub}

   * A lot of bugs removed.

   + Added support for multiple guide files: when a guide file refer to another one in a link button,
     the referred one is converted too recursively.

   - The main html file is now named exactly as the original guide file, suffixed by ".html".
     (That is needed by the support for multiples guide files).

@{b}* Version 1.23 @{i}(23.11.1997)@{ui} :@{ub}

   * Bugs removed.

   * Improved AmigaGuide compatibility (again :-)): supports fg and bg commands and others...

@{b}* Version 1.221 @{i}(21.11.1997)@{ui} :@{ub}

   * Bug removed when [CANCEL] button was clicked in the ASL requesters.

@{b}* Version 1.22 @{i}(20.11.1997)@{ui} :@{ub}

   * Improved AmigaGuide compatibility.

   * Corrected the output directory options (it was not functionnal).

   - Added some options (text, link, vlink, alink).

   - The help file is now available in html format (see html dir). :-)

@{b}* Version 1.21 @{i}(28.10.1997)@{ui} :@{ub}

   - Added a output directory gadget and option.

@{b}* Version 1.2 @{i}(24.6.1997)@{ui} :@{ub}

   - Added a Workbench interface.

@{b}* Version 1.1 @{i}(7.6.1997)@{ui} :@{ub}

   * All Enforcer HITs found where removed (and there was a lot because I've forgotten to run it
     for the previous version ;-0

   - Better support for symbols '@' and '<' and '>'

@{b}* Version 1.0 @{i}(3.6.1997)@{ui} :@{ub}

   First realised version.

@endnode
